|             ___  _|                      |_                  |
|         --> NMI |_|2                   39|_| XTAL <--        |
|             ___  _|                      |_                  |
|         --> IRQ |_|3                   38|_| EXTAL <--       |
|            ____  _|                      |_  _____           |
|        --> FIRQ |_|4                   37|_| Reset <--       |
|                  _|                      |_                  |
|          <-- BS |_|5                   36|_| MRDY <--        |
|                  _|                      |_                  |
|          <-- BA |_|6                   35|_| Q -->           |
|                  _|                      |_                  |
|             Vcc |_|7                   34|_| E -->           |
|                  _|                      |_  ___ ____        |
|          <-- A0 |_|8                   33|_| DMA/BREQ <--    |
|                  _|                      |_    _             |
|          <-- A1 |_|9                   32|_| R/W -->         |
|                  _|                      |_                  |
|          <-- A2 |_|10       6809       31|_| D0 <-->         |
|                  _|                      |_                  |
